 Geordie Greep（以前是Black Midi）分享了折衷的新单曲“布鲁斯” https://www.nme.com/news/music/geordie/geordie-greep-formerly-of-black-midi-shares-clectic-new-new-new-single-new-single-blues-3798648?utm_source=rsss = rsss＆utm_medium_medium = rsss间黑色 - 米迪 - 份额新闻蓝调Anagricel DuranTue, 01 Oct 2024 14:07:11 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3798648 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Geordie Greep。图片来源：是的孩子" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌标志着音乐家即将发行的专辑“ The New Sound”的第二首曲目</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/geordie-greep-formerly-of-black-midi-shares-eclectic-new-single-blues-3798648">Geordie Greep（以前是Black Midi）分享了折衷的新单曲“ Blues”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Geordie Greep。图片来源：是的孩子" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Geordie-Greep">Geordie Greep</a>在即将发行的首张个人专辑“ The New Sound”中分享了他折衷的新单曲“ Blues”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/geordie-greep-interview-black-midi-split-solo-album-new-sound-3790258">Geordie Greep谈论“新声音”和Black Midi Split：“我会做不同的事情”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这条曲目的开头是一个错误的开端，看到Greep演奏了一个快速而激烈的吉他即兴<em>即兴即兴即兴</em>演奏，然后用拉丁莎莎风格的各种乐器的疯狂混合体接管了他：<em>必须工作是因为工作是为schmucks的。”</em></p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/geordie-greep-blues-interview-black-midi-1235113175/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石乐队（Rolling Stone）</em></a>采访时谈到这首歌时，这位前<a href="/artists/Black-Midi">黑人中部</a>负责人分享道：“我想在那首歌中做一首歌，就像&#39;哦，看这个摇摇欲坠的人 - 然后，我们都有点摇摇欲坠。我们都已经18岁了。当您认为自己是狗屎时，我想做一首歌，当您沿着街上行走时，您会感到这种感觉，您可以想象这是一部电影。就像，真是个狂！实际上，这只是一堆有趣的线条，主题是18岁。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Geordie Greep-布鲁斯（电视眼睛直播）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gNGlbB4Gbyo?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>单曲标志着Greep即将发行的个人专辑的第二次产品。它遵循先前发行的主单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-midi-split-geordie-greep-announces-debut-solo-album-the-new-sound-with-single-holy-holy-3785237">圣洁</a>”。他的LP“新声音”定于本周五（10月4日）发布，<a href="https://geordiegreep.ffm.to/newsound" target="_blank" rel="noopener">可在此处预订 /预储备</a>。</p><p>谈到专辑在新闻稿中的创作时，Greep分享了：“录制&#39;新声音&#39;，这是我第一次没有人可以回答。而且，由于我的每一次冲动，我都能够完全遵循它的结论。在乐队（Black Midi）中，我们经常有这种“我们可以做一切”的感觉，但是您在这种方法上也有限，有时候做其他事情是很好的，可以放开事情。”</p><p>超过三十多名音乐家参与了在圣保罗和伦敦的两个大洲的专辑制作。 Greep解释说：“我们在其他地方已经录制的一些曲目，但这只是不对的，所以我们与新朋友重新录制了它们。”</p><p>他继续说：“一半的赛道是在巴西完成的，当地音乐家在最后一刻齐心协力。” “他们从未听说过我以前做过的任何事情，他们只是对我做的演示感兴趣。跟踪全部完成了，也许是两天。然后，我们稍后在伦敦进行了杂乱无章的工作。” </p><figure id="attachment_3798665" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3798665" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3798665" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Geordie Greep“ The New Sound”专辑艺术品。信用出版社" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3798665" class="wp-caption-text"> Geordie Greep“ The New Sound”专辑艺术品。信用出版社</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>Geordie Greep“新声音”曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1.&#39;Blues&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>2。&#39;Terra&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>3。“圣洁，圣洁”</strong><br /> <strong>4。“新声音”</strong><br /> <strong>5。“走路”</strong><br /> <strong>6。“通过战争”</strong><br /> <strong>7。“邦戈季节”</strong><br /> <strong>8。&#39;摩托车&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>9。&#39;好像华尔兹&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>10。“魔术师”</strong><br /> <strong>11。&#39;如果你只是一个梦</strong></p><p>这位音乐家的独奏作品宣布是在Greep和他的前队友Cameron Picton <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-midi-are-indefinitely-over-confirms-bassist-and-frontman-3782676">在社交媒体上证实了Black Midi的“无限期”结束</a>之后的几天。</p><p>在Instagram的直播中，Greep回应了粉丝，询问乐队何时通过在聊天中键入“ No More Midi”和“ It Over”来发行新专辑。</p><p>他继续说道：“黑色MIDI是一个有趣的乐队，现在已经无限期地结束了。”</p><p>这位歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/geordie-greep-interview-black-midi-split-solo-album-new-sound-3790258">与<em>NME</em>谈到有关“新声音”的工作时</a>透露，这是“我第一次对我喜欢听的音乐非常透明到。”</p><p>他告诉<em>NME：</em> “我喜欢在黑色MIDI中，但这些歌曲使自己与不同的人一起演奏。” “此外，我想开始做更多以我自己的名字的事情，然后尝试更通用的东西。我知道我最终想这样做。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_lpSYkM85r/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148